headline: Award-winning Actress Hannah Waddingham Brings the Magic of "The Love Boat" Back to Life in New Princess Cruises Ad Campaign
summary: Princess Cruises is setting sail on a wave of nostalgia and star power with its new global advertising campaign, "Love Boat by Hannah," featuring Ted Lasso's Emmy-winning actress and musical theater sensation Hannah Waddingham. Bringing her powerhouse vocals and signature charm, Waddingham reintroduces audiences to one of TV's most recognizable theme songs: The Love Boat.
